text:
Hazuki-san
Can I borrow your copier for a minute...?

Sure, it's fine~
What is it for?

I think Tenka-chan lost her prints and
she needs them right away.

Amana has the same one,
so I wanted to copy that for her.

Oh, I see~
Then let's print it right away.

Please tell Tenka-san not to
lose it again~

Yes!
Amana will tell her exactly what you said!
